Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.43,0:00:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找吧  收集梦想的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.70,0:00:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无奈也能感受到此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表看起来更单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法坦诚表达心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.19,0:00:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把想说的话收藏在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.53,0:00:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今更不能说出幼稚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.94,0:00:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好说时间能解决一切 却怕无人能懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.48,0:00:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天24小时我都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是司空见惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.46,0:01:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是嘲笑着匆匆而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.53,0:01:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其执着回忆 不如寻找现在的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.70,0:01:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好担心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.13,0:01:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为戈薇再也不回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不好好的跟戈薇道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.94,0:01:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗唆耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.41,0:01:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人是怎么搞定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.65,0:02:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  八成是\N戈薇姑娘愿意妥协吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许犬夜叉和桔梗劈腿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.82,0:02:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇居然能忍受这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为犬夜叉太会钻牛角尖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.63,0:02:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在穷追猛打我想不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他从平常就没从容过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他也有点不安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.31,0:02:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第49话  琥珀失去的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是奈落的城的遗迹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还残留着些许奈落的瘴气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.51,0:02:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连点痕迹都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的有座城才是怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是  现在回想起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.89,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也是把我们\N诱骗到假的城里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.96,0:03:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时看到的城是幻觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落之城的确曾经在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  找到什么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家父的铠甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.15,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我们这些驱魔师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被诱骗到奈落城里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞来骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我也来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  家父与同伴惨遭杀害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.91,0:04:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手的人  是我的弟弟琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子受奈落所操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸首就埋在庭院的一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.55,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.93,0:05:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让令尊与大家的遗骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弃置在这种不祥之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把他们\N带到适当的地点好好供奉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.57,0:05:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.78,0:05:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说这里就是奈落的城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城中的那些人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.86,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚那\N受奈落所控制的弟弟琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会也跟着城堡一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不会被野狗挖出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就请各位安眠于此吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在我们的村子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的为各位造墓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然村子里已经没有人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还有我与琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人可以守着坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是琥珀他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子  手艺真不赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.36,0:06:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的看得很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.86,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还让你帮忙砍柴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你也累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.87,0:06:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到屋里喝点东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  有想起什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.61,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是自己从哪来之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最起码该知道自己的名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在这个城附近的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.69,0:07:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概十天前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人见大人的城仿佛失踪般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失的无影无踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天就发现你倒在旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.41,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是经历什么很可怕的遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.14,0:07:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会什么都忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系  别着急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对  在你想起来之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢怎样都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  还有这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量多吃点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.17,0:08:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我似乎曾在那里待过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公公  老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以千万不要出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们这段时间的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.77,0:08:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从城里逃出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天  城消失的晚上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没有活下去的必要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你父亲跟同伴的身边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫…琥珀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.47,0:09:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四魂碎片的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近了  就在森林那一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的目的也是四魂碎片吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.06,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.76,0:09:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  把埋在你体内的\N四魂之玉碎片交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.54,0:09:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把碎片交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.51,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.29,0:09:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妖怪想夺走\N琥珀体内的四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.46,0:09:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.89,0:10:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀的性命全靠\N埋在体内的四魂碎片维系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.53,0:10:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片一旦被取出…他就会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被奈落控制了心智…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在奈落的城里才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.56,0:10:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手腕受伤了  让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.72,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我以前见过你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从城里逃走前的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的都不记得了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连奈落也不记得?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没有活下去的必要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.47,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你父亲跟同伴的身边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  那就是奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子一定是在演戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看起来不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.55,0:11:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.39,0:11:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  以前出现在\N我们面前的琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛被抽走魂魄的傀儡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们两人独处不要紧吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.87,0:11:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为珊瑚说想和他独处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱魔师的村落?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.28,0:12:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我们以前住在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我也能驱逐妖怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见习的程度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.39,0:12:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下  待会还得工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  你也准备一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经十一岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也差不多该参与实战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪真的会吐出火或毒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  你害怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们驱除的\N通常只是大蛇或大蜘蛛之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.57,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可怕的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些伪装成人形的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到四魂之玉的话就不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  被奈落叫去的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是琥珀第一次上阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你所知的  请全部告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛昔日的琥珀般…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖巧而有点胆小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.81,0:13:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点慢慢的回想就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今后我们会一直在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.02,0:13:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得不太好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好害羞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是姐弟呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从奈落的手里逃出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扁他两三拳不就现出原形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这么简单吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管这是不是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日最疼爱的弟弟已经回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是陷阱的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚会大受打击的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.30,0:14:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为奈落\N最喜欢玩弄人的感情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.68,0:14:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都不说的话  我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等不要这样子  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…关于琥珀的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.86,0:15:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奈落的陷阱不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.77,0:15:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是想要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我除了相信还能怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奈落的技俩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不是我们及时赶到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片被抽出来话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.01,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟就会真的死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.25,0:15:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  这就是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.35,0:15:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好像因为\N自己在这里的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而害那个温柔的人遭遇不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是太疼弟弟才分不清道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗唆  你懂什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好给我认清现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且本来就是犬夜叉你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是一大群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.76,0:16:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的手下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们难道是针对琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.68,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片的气息移动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.69,0:16:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要保护琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.81,0:16:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  你想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们将琥珀藏起来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.95,0:17:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想装蒜  他是奈落养的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.92,0:17:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀那家伙竟然趁乱逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.62,0:17:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片还在他身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是来带他回去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈落也真是小题大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.60,0:17:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过想要四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就带这么庞大的阵仗来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说目标是四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不过没了那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.64,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀就会没命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体就丢给他姐姐珊瑚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.86,0:18:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么追来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的目标是我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.44,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  不要再离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.95,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.98,0:18:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对我这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我唯一的亲弟弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  琥珀交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去阻止它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.82,0:19:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  你一定要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.78,0:19:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有箭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲到那个洞里去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在犬夜叉他们来之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先待在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.46,0:20:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  珊瑚很强的  不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.83,0:20:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀  你还没想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.07,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚是你姐姐的事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好怀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.01,0:20:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚被迫和你分开后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.35,0:20:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间一直很担心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她平常很坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有时也会露出落寞的神情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.03,0:21:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以琥珀回来真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.10,0:21:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以和她在一起吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.14,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话\N你就能想起她的一切了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.04,0:21:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能想起那个人的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.05,0:21:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么可怕的东西\N我非想起来不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.06,0:21:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她  杀了戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.86,0:21:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉好慢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.17,0:21:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破魔之矢用光了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.80,0:22:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了真正重要的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.28,0:22:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能舍弃其他一切就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.32,0:22:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而现实却是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.63,0:22:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的时刻只要随时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.33,0:22:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.14,0:23:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海浮现你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.71,0:23:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-但愿直到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.22,0:23:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远沉睡的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.69,0:23:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.00,0:23:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不止息存在我心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.32,0:23:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆被消除的琥珀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.09,0:23:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然受奈落的操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.19,0:23:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实行奈落命令杀害戈薇的琥珀
